Some financial functions for Yii framework.

1. Copy file of class "LoansHelper.php" to "protected/helpres/" directory of your project

2. In config:
	...
	'import' => array(
		...
		'application.helpers.*',
		...
	),
	...

3. Example of use:
	LoansHelper::annuity_payment( 12000, 6, 36 );


Function list:

Methods:
	annuity_payment
	payments_graph_annuity
	payments_graph_diff
	PSK